name: Home of Dmitry's Projects
body:
### Welcome to Home of Dmitry's Projects.
Here are the projects I've been working on recently:
* [redux-actions-assertions](https://www.npmjs.com/package/redux-actions-assertions) - the library that adds assertions for redux actions testing.
* [vagrantfile-windows-iis-mssql](https://github.com/dmitry-zaets/vagrantfile-windows-iis-mssql) - Vagrantfile for testing ASP.NET (MVC) Websites on Windows.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
